Epic Threads
''See also [[thread]] and [[posting in an epic thread]].''

Not to be confused with a stylin' Frank Sinatra suit from the '60s, '''EPIC THREADS''' are [[EPIC]]. Some are short and sweet, defining the essence of [[B|/b/]], whilst others are [[verbose thread|verbose]] because of the way they are played in a [[MPG]] style. And then, there's always the stoopid and [[ironic]].

